\section{CELLxGENE Census workflow}{

CELLxGENE Census exposes 60M+ cells as a single SOMA experiment hosted
on public S3 (\code{s3://cellxgene-census-public-us-west-2/}).
\code{readSOMA()} can stream a filtered slice directly via
